The nine elixirs are:
First, Elixir Radiance;
Second, Divine Talisman;
Third, Divine Elixir;
Fourth, Reverted Elixir;
Fifth, Ingested Elixir;
Sixth, Refined Elixir;
Seventh, Malleable Elixir;
Eighth, Subdued Elixir;
Ninth, Cold Elixir.

Another song said:
*"Round as three-five, a tenth of an inch.
Mouth four-eight, lips two inches.
Two feet long, thickness even.
Belly threefold aligned, seated warmth enduring."*
